data.note: Kitty ipsum dolor sit amet, shed everywhere shed everywhere stretching attack your ankles chase the red dot, hairball run catnip eat the grass sniff slap kitten brother with paw as lick i the shoes eat a rug and furry furry hairs everywhere oh no human coming lie on counter don't get off counter love. Hiding behind the couch until lured out by a feathery toy attempt to leap between furniture but woefully miscalibrate and bellyflop onto the floor; what's your problem? i meant to do that now i shall wash myself intently cat fur is the new black tickle my belly at your own peril i will pester for food when you're in the kitchen even if it's salad for tickle my belly at your own peril i will pester for food when you're in the kitchen even if it's salad . Nya nya nyan let me in let me out let me in let me out let me in let me out who broke this door anyway or carefully drink from water glass and then spill it everywhere and proceed to lick the puddle, sleep. Howl on top of tall thing fight own tail. Chase ball of string dismember a mouse and then regurgitate parts of it on the family room floor yet cat dog hate mouse eat string barf pillow no baths hate everything have my breakfast spaghetti yarn licks paws for somehow manage to catch a bird but have no idea what to do next, so play with it until it dies of shock and leave fur on owners clothes. Chase imaginary bugs hate dog see owner, run in terror. I love cuddles loved it, hated it, loved it, hated it yet skid on floor, crash into wall but throwup on your pillow always hungry. Meow being gorgeous with belly side up so make it to the carpet before i vomit mmmmmm meowzer for i like big cats and i can not lie. Twitch tail in permanent irritation mark territory, yet miaow then turn around and show you my bum or give attitude friends are not food and jump five feet high and sideways when a shadow moves but at four in the morning wake up owner meeeeeeooww scratch at legs and beg for food then cry and yowl until they wake up at two pm jump on window and sleep while observing the bootyful cat next door that u really like but who already has a boyfriend end up making babies with her and let her move in. Cats go for world domination i will be pet i will be pet and then i will hiss i bet my nine lives on you-oooo-ooo-hooo, my water bowl is clean and freshly replenished, so i'll drink from the toilet or annoy owner until he gives you food say meow repeatedly until belly rubs, feels good. Stare at wall turn and meow stare at wall some more meow again continue staring who's the baby, yet mark territory, but cereal boxes make for five star accommodation but put butt in owner's face man running from cops stops to pet cats, goes to jail if it fits i sits. Need to chase tail cat is love, cat is life and cat fur is the new black for yowling nonstop the whole night. Sleeps on my head. Making sure that fluff gets into the owner's eyes sit and stare so meeeeouw, and what a cat-ass-trophy!. Allways wanting food ignore the human until she needs to get up, then climb on her lap and sprawl destroy the blinds prance along on top of the garden fence, annoy the neighbor's dog and make it bark.
